<h1>Help</h1>

<h3>How do I add content to the site?</h3>
<p>If a place already exists, you can't edit the information for that place unless you're the owner of that place. However, if theres something wrong with the information on that place then send us a report using the link on the place's page.</p>
<p>If you'd like to submit a new place, you can submit a request for a new place and fill in as much information as you know about that place using the submit stuff link at the top of ther page or click <a href="/submitStuff.html" title="Submit Stuff">here</a></p>
<h3>What if I can't find what I'm looking for?</h3>
<p>If you can't find the information you're looking for then send us a <a href="/contact.html" title="Contact Us">comment</a>, and we'll try and help as much as we can. If the place doesn't exist in our records, you could always add it yourself</p>
<h3>How do I edit an existing entry?</h3>
<p>Unfortunately, unless you're the owner of the place that needs editing, you can't edit an existing entry. However you can report a location to us to give us more information on that place.</p>
<h3>How do I write a review?</h3>
<p>If you'd like to review a place, then go to that place's information page and submit a new review at the bottom of that page.</p>
<h3>How do I add a new location?</h3>
<p>If you're in a location where we have no information and you'd like to use this service, please get in <a href="contact.html" title="Contact Us">contact</a> with us.</p>
<h3>Is there a possibility for new categories?</h3>
<p>Of course theres the possibility of adding a new category. We're forever growing and you'd like to give us some information on a place but we haven't got the relevant category as an option, get in <a href="contact.html">contact</a> with us as we'll help as much as possible</p>
<h3>How do I add a new image or menu for a place</h3>
<p>If you go to the specific place's information page, there is a link to be able to upload a new image or menu, or even give us a web address of an existing menu online.</p>
